  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2010-07-28",
    "date": "2010-08-05T13:16:59Z",
    "text": "Commends the government of Japan for extending an official apology to all U.S. former prisoners of war from the Pacific War and planning to invite surviving members to Japan.\n\nRequests that the government of Japan respect the wishes and sensibilities of these prisoners of war by providing an appropriate program for lasting remembrance and reconciliation that recognizes their sacrifices and forced labor.\n\nAcknowledges the Department of State's work in advocating for these prisoners.\n\nApplauds the dedication and patriotism of the members and descendants of the American Defenders of Bataan and Corregidor for their pursuit of justice and lasting peace."
  },
